   coupled to graphical presentation capabilities                 6834 1451
   (code ZVView by V. Zerkin) through the chain of                6834 1451
   PrePro codes by D. Cullen                                      6834 1451
 - ENDF checking codes (CHECKR, FIZCON, PSYCHE)                   6834 1451
 - Highly automated fitting of optical model                      6834 1451
   parameters (by B.V. Carlson)                                   6834 1451
 - KALMAN code for fitting experimental data and                  6834 1451
